name: Computhink
overview:
Computhink is the developer of the ViewWise Document Management System, assisting small to medium-sized organizations improve efficiency across all departments. The ViewWise Document Management System has already saved organizations across all industries millions of dollars in time, business process improvements, and paper, printing, and storage costs. ViewWise can be deployed in multiple environments and even accessed via the web (and the latest smartphone technology) through ViewWise Web Access (which works on tablets such as the Apple iPad) and ViewWise Online options.

ViewWise products adhere to industry standards and facilitate seamless integration with existing hardware and software installations utilizing Java server-based technology. The ViewWise Document Management System is delployed in various vertical markets such as Accounting, A/E/C, Accounts Payable / Accounts Receivable, Education, Financial Services, Manufacturing, Government, Healthcare, Legal, Manufacturing, Non-Profits, Real Estate, and Transportation.
